What year did Chelsea win their first European title?

Participants with the correct answer will be entered into a final draw on 31 July 2025.

Terms and conditions* apply.

*Giveaway T&Cs:

Open to UAE residents aged 18+ only
One entry per person
Prize: CFC Jersey with DAMAC logo
17 winners will be picked randomly on 31 July 2025
Emirates ID required to claim the prize
Entry closes on 27 July 2025
This promotion is licensed by Dubai Economy & Tourism (Permit No. COP-25-080627)
Prize is non-transferable & non-redeemable for cash
Not associated with Instagram or Facebook
